y:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">出品，必属精品</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":48849,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-29 16:26:46","updateTime":"2019-06-29 16:26:46","isTrue":false,"questionId":10932,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">患处痛觉迟钝</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":48850,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-29 16:26:46","updateTime":"2019-06-29 16:26:46","isTrue":false,"questionId":10932,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">愈后一般无色素沉着</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":48851,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-29 16:26:46","updateTime":"2019-06-29 16:26:46","isTrue":true,"questionId":10932,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">如不感染，</span>1-2周内愈合</span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":48852,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-29 16:26:46","updateTime":"2019-06-29 16:26:46","isTrue":false,"questionId":10932,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">未伤及皮肤的真皮层</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":48853,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-29 16:26:46","updateTime":"2019-06-29 16:26:46","isTrue":false,"questionId":10932,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">愈后常有瘢痕增生</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":929,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:30","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:30","name":"171","questionCnt":150,"tagTypeId":46},{"id":983,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:36:21","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:36:21","name":"其他A2","questionCnt":19,"tagTypeId":47}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":2398,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:46:30","topicId":null,"tagId":927,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":98,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">女</span>,28岁，工人，扎辫。工作时不慎致头皮撕脱，查体:痛苦面容，半侧颅骨(仅存骨膜)裸露，创面及撕脱的头皮清洁。其最理想的处理方法是</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">头皮撕脱伤应根据伤后时间撕脱是否完全、撕脱头皮的条件、颅骨是否裸露、创面有无感染征象等情况采用不同的方法处理</span>:①若皮瓣尚未完全脱离且血供尚好，可在细致清创后原位缝合。②如皮瓣已完全脱落,但完整,无明显污染，血管断端整齐，且伤后未超过6小时,可在清创后试行头皮血管(颞浅动、静脉或枕动、静脉)吻合,再全层缝合撕脱的头皮；如因条件所限,不能采用此法，则需将撕脱的头皮瓣切薄成类似的中厚皮片，置于骨膜上，再缝合包扎。③如撕脱的皮瓣挫伤或污染较重已不能利用,而骨膜尚未撕脱，又不能作转移皮瓣时，可取腹部或大腿中厚皮片作游离植皮;若骨膜已遭破坏，颅骨外露，可先作局部筋膜转移,再植皮。④伤后已久，创面已有感染或经上述处理失败者,只能行创面清洁和更换敷料,待肉芽组织生长后再行邮票状植皮。如颅骨裸露，还需作多处颅骨钻孔至板障层,等钻孔处长出肉芽后再植皮。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":6277,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:46:30","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:46:30","isTrue":false,"questionId":2398,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">在颅骨上钻孔、待肉芽生长后植皮</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6278,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:46:30","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:46:30","isTrue":false,"questionId":2398,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">行头皮血管吻合再植</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6279,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:46:30","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:46:30","isTrue":false,"questionId":2398,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">将撕脱的头皮直接缝回</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6280,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:46:30","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:46:30","isTrue":false,"questionId":2398,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">将脱的头皮做成全厚皮片植回</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6281,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:46:30","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:46:30","isTrue":true,"questionId":2398,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">将撕脱的头皮做成中厚皮片植回</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":983,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:36:21","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:36:21","name":"其他A2","questionCnt":19,"tagTypeId":47},{"id":927,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","name":"181","questionCnt":150,"tagTypeId":46}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":2386,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:41:39","topicId":null,"tagId":927,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":94,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">女，</span>3岁，右手中指疼痛1个月。查体:中指屈曲，不能伸直，掌指关节掌侧处可触及0.3m×0.3cm大小硬结，压痛，可随屈肌腱上下活动。首选的治疗方法是</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">小儿拇长屈肌腱鞘炎常为双侧性</span>,表现为拇指屈伸时发生弹响，或指间关节交锁于屈曲位，掌指关节皮下可触及痛性结节。（1）局部制动和腱鞘内注射醋酸泼尼松龙或复方倍他米松有很好疗效。但注射一定要准确，可直接注射到腱鞘邻近的骨膜附近,注入皮下则无效,一旦注入桡动脉浅支,则有可能发生桡侧三个手指血管痉挛或栓塞导致指端坏死。（2）非手术治疗无效时可考虑行狭窄的腱鞘切开减压术:注意牵开切口两侧的皮神经和血管,充分暴露腱鞘。此时被动活动病人手指,可见到膨大的结节在腱鞘狭窄处上、下移动。认准腱鞘狭窄增厚范围,用尖刀沿着肌腱方向纵向从一侧切开腱鞘.切开范围要足够长，再将切开的腱鞘的两侧各剪去约0.3cm,以彻底解除狭窄避免复发。如仅行狭窄处切开,有时会发生再粘连而症状复发。（3）小儿先天性狭窄性腱鞘炎非手术治疗通常无效,应行手术治疗。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":6217,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:41:39","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:41:39","isTrue":false,"questionId":2386,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">局部封闭治疗</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6218,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:41:39","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:41:39","isTrue":false,"questionId":2386,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">手术治疗</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6219,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:41:39","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:41:39","isTrue":false,"questionId":2386,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">口服非甾体抗炎药</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6220,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:41:39","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:41:39","isTrue":true,"questionId":2386,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">局部制动</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6221,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:41:39","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:41:39","isTrue":false,"questionId":2386,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">物理治疗</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":983,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:36:21","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:36:21","name":"其他A2","questionCnt":19,"tagTypeId":47},{"id":927,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","name":"181","questionCnt":150,"tagTypeId":46}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":2357,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:30:47","topicId":null,"tagId":927,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":88,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">女，</span>40岁。1小时前服敌百虫200ml,查体:躁动，瞳孔缩小，四肢强直、肺部可闻及湿啰音。下列处理措施不恰当的是</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">记忆：敌百虫禁用碳酸氢钠洗胃。立即将患者撤离中毒现场。彻底清除未被机体吸收入血的毒物</span>,如迅速脱去污染衣服,用肥皂水清洗污染皮肤、毛发和指甲；眼部污染时,用清水、生理盐水、2%碳酸氢钠溶液或3%硼酸溶液冲洗。口服中毒者,用清水、2%碳酸氢钠溶液(敌百虫中毒者忌用)或1:5000高锰酸钾溶液(对硫磷中毒者忌用)反复洗胃,即首次洗胃后保留胃管，间隔3-4小时重复洗胃,直至洗出液清亮为止。然后用硫酸钠20-40g溶于20ml水，口服,观察30分钟,无导泻作用时，再口服或经鼻胃管注人水500ml。洗胃后,灌入泻药以清除肠道内毒物。一般不用油脂类泻药,以免促进脂溶性毒物吸收。导泻常用聚乙二醇、硫酸钠或硫酸镁,口服或由胃管注人。镁离子吸收过多对中枢神经系统有抑制作用。肾或呼吸衰竭、昏迷和磷化锌、OPI中毒晚期者不宜使用。解毒药应用阿托品和解磷定。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":6072,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:30:47","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:30:47","isTrue":false,"questionId":2357,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">药物导泻</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6073,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:30:47","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:30:47","isTrue":false,"questionId":2357,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">清洗呕吐物污染的皮肤</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6074,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:30:47","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:30:47","isTrue":false,"questionId":2357,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">静脉应用阿托品</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6075,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:30:47","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:30:47","isTrue":false,"questionId":2357,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">应用解磷定</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6076,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:30:47","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:30:47","isTrue":true,"questionId":2357,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\">2%碳酸氢钠溶液洗胃</span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":983,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:36:21","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:36:21","name":"其他A2","questionCnt":19,"tagTypeId":47},{"id":927,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","name":"181","questionCnt":150,"tagTypeId":46}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":2307,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:07:49","topicId":null,"tagId":927,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":76,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">女，</span>35岁。左手示指末节肿胀、疼痛3天。3天前洗鱼时被鱼刺扎伤左手示指末节。起病时指尖有针刺样疼痛，轻度肿胀，继而肿胀明显加重，有剧烈的跳痛。查体T37.9℃，左示指末节肿胀明显，指腹张力明显增高，触痛明显。血常规:WBC13.0×10</span><sup><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px;vertical-align:super\">9</span></sup><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\">/L，N 0.89。如行手术治疗，正确的操作是</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">脓性指头炎：为手指末节掌面的皮下化脓性细菌感染</span>,多因甲沟炎加重或指尖、手指末节皮肤受伤后引起。致病菌多为金黄色葡萄球菌。初起阶段,指头有针刺样痛,轻度肿胀。继而指头肿胀加重、有剧烈的跳痛,可有发热、全身不适、白细胞计数增高。感染加重时,神经末梢因受压和营养障碍而麻痹,指头疼痛反而减轻;皮色由红转白，反映局部组织趋于坏死;若末节指骨并发骨髓炎,化脓指头破溃溢脓后,因指骨坏死或骨髓炎创口常经久不愈。指头炎初发时,应悬吊前臂平置患手,避免下垂以减轻疼痛。给予青霉素等抗菌药物，以金黄散糊剂敷贴患指。若患指剧烈疼痛、肿胀明显、伴有全身症状，应当及时切开引流，以免指骨受压坏死和发生骨髓炎。通常采用指神经阻滞麻醉，选用末节指侧面作纵切口,切口远侧不超过甲沟的1/2，近侧不超过指节横纹,将皮下纤维索分离切断,剪去突出的脂肪使引流通畅；脓腔较大则宜作对口引流，切口内放置橡皮片引流,有死骨片应当除去；切口不应做成鱼口形，以免术后瘢痕形成影响手指触觉。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":5823,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:07:49","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:07:49","isTrue":true,"questionId":2307,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">脓腔较大可做对口引流</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":5824,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:07:49","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:07:49","isTrue":false,"questionId":2307,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">在末节指腹正中作纵切口</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":5825,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:07:49","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:07:49","isTrue":false,"questionId":2307,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">切口远侧应超过甲沟的</span>1/2</span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":5826,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:07:49","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:07:49","isTrue":false,"questionId":2307,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">切口近侧应超过指节横纹</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":5827,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:07:49","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:07:49","isTrue":false,"questionId":2307,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">切口要做成鱼口形</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":983,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:36:21","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:36:21","name":"其他A2","questionCnt":19,"tagTypeId":47},{"id":927,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","name":"181","questionCnt":150,"tagTypeId":46}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":2295,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:02:41","topicId":null,"tagId":927,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":72,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">女，</span>56岁。全身麻醉下行右乳癌改良根治术术后2小时。查体: T36.9℃, P85次/分，R21次/分，BP130/85mmHg,意识清醒。此时宜采取的体位是</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">乳癌术后，采用高半卧位，半卧位有利于血液循环，并增加肺潮气量。半卧位可减轻腹部张力，使病人舒适，因为这种卧位可以减少腹部肌肉牵拉受力，减少病人的疼痛及伤口缝线张力</span>,有利于引流，故本题选E。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":5763,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:02:41","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:02:41","isTrue":false,"questionId":2295,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">斜坡卧位</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":5764,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:02:41","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:02:41","isTrue":false,"questionId":2295,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">仰卧位</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":5765,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:02:41","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:02:41","isTrue":false,"questionId":2295,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">头低脚高位</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":5766,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:02:41","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:02:41","isTrue":false,"questionId":2295,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">侧卧位</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":5767,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:02:41","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:02:41","isTrue":true,"questionId":2295,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">高半坐位卧式</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":983,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:36:21","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:36:21","name":"其他A2","questionCnt":19,"tagTypeId":47},{"id":927,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","name":"181","questionCnt":150,"tagTypeId":46}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":2288,"createTime":"2019-06-20 08:58:36","topicId":null,"tagId":927,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":69,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">男，</span>50岁。干农活时刺伤右足10天，当时未就医，伤口已愈合良好，伤口内无异物残留。感张口困难2天，颈项紧，饮水可诱发手足痉挛，病情逐渐加重，抽搐频繁，用药物未控制，呼吸道分泌物较多，有窒息的危险，为保持呼吸道的通畅，最有效的措施是</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">足外伤史</span>+张口困难=破伤风。破伤风患者痉挛发作频繁不易控制者，可用硫喷妥钠缓慢静注，但要警惕发生喉头痉挛和呼吸抑制，用于已作气管切开者比较安全。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":5728,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 08:58:36","updateTime":"2019-06-20 08:58:36","isTrue":false,"questionId":2288,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">协助拍背咳痰咳液</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":5729,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 08:58:36","updateTime":"2019-06-20 08:58:36","isTrue":false,"questionId":2288,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">环甲膜穿刺</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":5730,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 08:58:36","updateTime":"2019-06-20 08:58:36","isTrue":false,"questionId":2288,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">气管插管</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":5731,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 08:58:36","updateTime":"2019-06-20 08:58:36","isTrue":true,"questionId":2288,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">气管切开</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":5732,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 08:58:36","updateTime":"2019-06-20 08:58:36","isTrue":false,"questionId":2288,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">吸痰、吸氧</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":983,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:36:21","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:36:21","name":"其他A2","questionCnt":19,"tagTypeId":47},{"id":927,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","name":"181","questionCnt":150,"tagTypeId":46}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":1924,"createTime":"2019-06-19 15:15:22","topicId":null,"tagId":931,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":99,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">女，</span>30岁。甲状腺肿大，性情急躁2年。查体：T37℃，P116次/分，R22次/分，BP130/60mmHg，甲状腺弥漫性3度肿大，甲状腺区域听诊可闻及低调的连续性静脉“嗡嗡”音。实验室检查：FT3、FT4均增高，TSH降低。既往曾服用硫脲类药物治疗，效果不佳，拟行手术治疗。目前单用碘剂进行术前准备，但基础代谢控制不满意，为做好术前准备可联合使用</span></p><p><br/></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">解析：普萘洛尔法</span>:对于常规应用硫氧嘧啶类药物不能耐受或无效者、碘剂过敏者，可单用普萘洛尔做术前准备。普萘洛尔是一种肾上腺素能 R 受体拮抗剂，能控制甲亢的症状，缩短术前准备的时间，且用药后不引起腺体充血，有利于手术操作，用法为每 6 小时 1 次，每次 20～60mg 口服。一般 4～7 日后脉率降至正常水平时，便可施行手术。由于普萘洛尔在体内的有效半衰期不到 8 小时，所以最末一次口服普萘洛尔要在术前 1～2 小时;术后继续逐渐减量应用普萘洛尔 4～7 日。此外，术前不用阿托品，以免引起心动过速。有哮喘病和心脏病者禁用此法。</span></p><p><br/></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":3915,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 15:15:22","updateTime":"2019-06-19 15:15:22","isTrue":false,"questionId":1924,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">苯巴比妥钠</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":3916,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 15:15:22","updateTime":"2019-06-19 15:15:22","isTrue":false,"questionId":1924,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">氯丙嗪</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":3917,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 15:15:22","updateTime":"2019-06-19 15:15:22","isTrue":false,"questionId":1924,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">氢化可的松</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":3918,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 15:15:22","updateTime":"2019-06-19 15:15:22","isTrue":false,"questionId":1924,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">胍乙啶</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":3919,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 15:15:22","updateTime":"2019-06-19 15:15:22","isTrue":true,"questionId":1924,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">普萘洛尔</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":983,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:36:21","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:36:21","name":"其他A2","questionCnt":19,"tagTypeId":47},{"id":931,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:38","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:38","name":"161","questionCnt":150,"tagTypeId":46}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":1901,"createTime":"2019-06-19 15:04:11","topicId":null,"tagId":931,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":95,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">女，</span>18岁。因多食、多饮、多尿、消瘦，诊断为I型糖尿病，给予胰岛素治疗，清晨出现出汗、心悸，继而意识障碍，最可能的原因是</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">解析：胰岛素和胰岛素类似物的常见不良反应是低血糖，与药物剂量过大、运动过量、进食过少有关，尤其接受强化治疗者更常见，低血糖表现为心悸、出汗、手抖、头晕、饥饿感、软弱，严重者出现精神症状和昏迷。少见不良反应有脂肪萎缩和过敏反应。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\">&nbsp;</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":3800,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 15:04:11","updateTime":"2019-06-19 15:04:11","isTrue":true,"questionId":1901,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">低血糖昏迷</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":3801,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 15:04:11","updateTime":"2019-06-19 15:04:11","isTrue":false,"questionId":1901,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">乳酸酸中毒</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":3802,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 15:04:11","updateTime":"2019-06-19 15:04:11","isTrue":false,"questionId":1901,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">高渗高血糖综合征</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":3803,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 15:04:11","updateTime":"2019-06-19 15:04:11","isTrue":false,"questionId":1901,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">过敏性休克</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":3804,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 15:04:11","updateTime":"2019-06-19 15:04:11","isTrue":false,"questionId":1901,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">酮症酸中毒</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":983,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:36:21","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:36:21","name":"其他A2","questionCnt":19,"tagTypeId":47},{"id":931,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:38","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:38","name":"161","questionCnt":150,"tagTypeId":46}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null}]}